Package keystone.api.wrappers.entities

Class Entity

java.lang.Object
keystone.api.wrappers.entities.Entity
public class Entity extends Object
A wrapper for a Minecraft entity. Contains information about the entity's NBT data

      public Entity data(String path, String data)

      Parameters:
      path - The NBT path. [e.g. "Items[0].Count", "Items[{Slot:0b}]"]
      data - The value to set. [e.g. "32b", "{id:"minecraft:diamond",Count:2b}"]
